            <title>[NIFI-7868] Processor Stats don&apos;t always include correct values for number of FlowFiles/Bytes sent</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NIFI-7868</link>
                <project id="12316020" key="NIFI">Apache NiFi</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a Processor emits a SEND provenance event, the framework keeps track of this, and shows this as one of the stats in the stats history. However, when a processor emits a SEND event with the &apos;force&apos; flag set to true (which is the default) such as PutFile, the values are not counted.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
